{"id":"04240d78-7af7-40a3-b737-22d8946516a4","title":"1509/01/27","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"44983e99-86ae-466c-9391-ce2967efd983","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, January 27th, [1509].","standoffProperties":[{"id":"b712a22c-aeae-4fd2-86f2-ea156d386162","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":3,"value":"8532f2fa-b614-4eed-9eae-586327f6a15a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"e7625210-f4ac-42fd-ae54-0d6b5f96c9cf","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"3100c68f-7cdb-41bb-9a50-57fb5dacaad5","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":30,"value":"5c616105-67ac-467a-a50f-8ba6ffd75865","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c8b1d678-bbac-416f-87c8-bde75e8c89f6","type":"style/superscript","start":21,"end":22,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"67191a75-2adc-4bf1-83e0-d3e195d9c7ac","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lodovico di Buonarrota Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"5ef32a5b-960c-4579-b1c2-ac85d25d1b77","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"250d0261-bc93-41c9-addd-5552caabe710","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"fb56e44b-83f5-40a8-9996-cd011a8f781c","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"8644f8fb-0e8e-40dd-9f93-f40529ddb08b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":1,"value":"0c663cc2-dd9f-40ce-b17b-734e41b369ef","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"453c0965-865e-461e-9562-5e3aa6235427","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"98a91f85-8ec1-4e83-85a5-8a2508d02ffc","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"c7dda8ee-68ca-4c72-9e9c-a260c29a10e3","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Dearest Father,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0I have to-day received a letter from you, and when I read it I was very much disturbed. I doubt that you are more timid and fearful\u00A0than the occasion warrants. I wish you would tell me what you think he could do\u2014the worst that could happen, that is, if he were to push matters to\u00A0extremes. I have no more to say about it. It grieves me that you should be possessed by this fear; wherefore I counsel you to be well prepared against his efforts, take wise advice, and then think no more\u00A0of the matter: for supposing he were to seize all you have in the world, you would not go short of comforts\u00A0and the means of subsistence, even if there were none\u00A0other left to you but myself. Therefore be of good cheer. I am still in great perplexity, for it is now a\u00A0year since I received the last grosso from this Pope, and I do not ask for any money because my work (*) is not progressing in such a manner as, in my opinion, to merit it. The cause lies in the difficulty of the work and the fact that it is not my profession. Thus I am wasting time fruitlessly. God help me!","standoffProperties":[{"id":"8640760a-17a9-4c42-a014-dd76f09a8603","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":13,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"9261b8a2-63a6-4c03-ad29-a004ff1b4a50","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":13,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"90a8ca83-a2a6-4283-92ec-9ea853580345","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":18,"end":18,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"6fe98a92-b6ed-4552-a27f-b8f331e0ba29","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":55,"end":57,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c1a09494-cd39-4d61-a780-3d6f31956a9f","type":"codex/entity-ref